# Portfolio Site Environment Variables

# Site Configuration
# -----------------
# The public URL where your site is deployed
# Used for SEO metadata, Open Graph tags, and canonical URLs
# Default: https://localhost:3000 (for local development)
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://your-domain.com

# Node Environment
# ---------------
# Automatically set by deployment platforms
# Options: development, production, test
# NODE_ENV=production

# Security
# --------
# Security headers (especially HSTS) are only enabled when NODE_ENV=production
# This prevents HTTPS enforcement during local development

# Future Configuration
